title: What Font Is This?
content:
Can someone please tell me what font this is?

 ![](http://web.archive.org/web/20131016015355im_/http:/typophile.com/files/etnoline_5444.jpg)

Thank you for your help!
author: fashionphoto

comments.content:
If some serifs are missing in your sample -due to small rendering size- it could be **[Ambroise Std Light](http://web.archive.org/web/20131016015355/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/typofonderie/ambroise-std/)** by Jean François Porchez (Typofonderie, 2001-2008)

EDIT: The /S looks different and /T width also does not match.
